own.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想完整咁睇又好散<br />\n好似法國既克洛維墨洛溫到卡佩王朝/波旁王朝<br />\n神羅建立前既歷史又好少<br />\n諾曼征服英格蘭前既又好少<br />\n西班牙係蠻族入侵後至被回教征服前既歷史<br />\n<br />\n要獨立每個國家歷史咁睇先睇到成個中世紀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5520fc73b7858e1c30458cfcef027468939e87a8","tid":999152,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50db8096b7c945a4c505f1021f0defefb2cc0dd8","tid":999152,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39a574b50f51b9744c202f8fc53e46133a204b7d","tid":999152,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T13:54:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T13:58:15.000Z","msg":"贖罪券<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T14:02:08.000Z","msg":"馬丁路德都中世紀末14世紀既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d7aee4ac1981b9da14881acb802d938cc4429fd","tid":999152,"uid":75594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T14:03:55.000Z","msg":"[歷史台]日不落的傳奇，大英帝國的故事<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/134149\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/134149</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e05a4630a0af6f6efada27f59ee729ba1f2d22a0","tid":999152,"uid":75594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T14:05:02.000Z","msg":"[歷史台]普魯士之逆襲，德國統一之路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/35798\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/35798</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fdc3451ded5c35e29721e73a007a72256ddec161","tid":999152,"uid":40478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e05a4630a0af6f6efada27f59ee729ba1f2d22a0","tid":999152,"uid":75594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T14:05:02.000Z","msg":"[歷史台]普魯士之逆襲，德國統一之路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/35798\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/35798</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T14:08:0